Roles &amp; Responsibilities

  Carry out breakdown repair and preventive maintenance of all equipment.&nbsp;
  Carry out the fabrication of equipment.&nbsp;
  carry out testing of equipment.&nbsp;
  Ensure safekeeping of hand tools and maintain good housekeeping.&nbsp;
  Ensure all works are carried out safely and/or in accordance with safety procedures.&nbsp;

Skills

  Proficient in English writing and speaking.
  Good technical experience and skillsets.&nbsp;
  Able to work and communicate well with others.&nbsp;
  Proficiency with hand tools.&nbsp;
